~ start
Nuclear war killed billions of people and destroyed the world. Step outside without proper equipment and you'll die fast.
There's barely any food or water. Everyone hides in their own shelters. The threat of bandits is high, thieves too. I almost got killed by one sneaking up behind me. 
Honestly, these sewers would be a good place to build a shelter. Lots of space. But the acid thats being drained here is deadly. Soon this place will be filled with it.
I hate to say it, but we're cooked.
=> END